data.description: Enjoy magnificent sunsets dance on the lake from the privacy of your balcony lanai. The breezes flow through this beautiful cathedral ceiling 2/2 condo with a breakfast bar kitchen and expansive great room. The main bedroom ensuite includes a walk-in closet, linen closet, and shower. The spacious guest bath includes a tub/shower. New A/C and replaced hot water heater. PLUS, one of the very few communities that include your own exterior storage closet just outside your front door! This intimate lakefront community features a covered carport and heated pool. The public Deep Creek Golf Club is just down the street! Come and see!
